-- China Huarong Sets Up Private Equity Fund in Chongqing, Securities Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-19T00:01:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/china-huarong-sets-up-private-equity-fund-in-chongqing-securities-reports.html

          
          
             - China Huarong Asset Management
Corp. formed a private equity fund with Chongqing Yufu Assets
Management Co., a local financing vehicle in the western
municipality, the China Securities Journal reported today,
citing Huarong.  
 The fund aims to raise 10 billion yuan, the newspaper said,
citing the company. Huarong owns a 70 percent stake in the fund
and Yufu has the remaining 30 percent stake, the newspaper said.  
